commit 5ca8e123bce61b275fbfb69fbb9ae6a90855096e
Author: rigley.costa <rigley.costa@grupomateus.com>
Date:   Sun Jul 19 10:57:14 2026 -0300

    fix(sync): rewrite pull cursor, remove Semaphore, simplify scheduler equality
    
    - Use last_synced_at as cursor instead of sending unsupported cursor field
      (was causing infinite pagination loop)
    - Replace custom Semaphore class with simple chunked Future.wait (groups of 2)
    - Use TaskData == structural equality instead of manual field diffing
    - Remove unused generation parameter from _exchangeNote

